text:
🌿🌾Community In Bloom Garden at Jurong Central Park is a green space managed by volunteers.
🌽🌶️🍆They come together to grow edible plants and share them with the group members and or with the community.
🦋🌹🪻Others may grow plants to support the Garden's biodiversity or share expertise on cultivating various orchids or bonsai.
🌿Community In Bloom is a program supported by NParks.
